title: Episode 20: Mosaic Sperm
itunes:title: Episode 20: Mosaic Sperm
description:
We bow down to the leprechaun.

Bobby and Khaly take a road trip to Arizona.

Khalyla's dream scenario involves a centipede.

We each choose three baby daddies whose sperm we'd like to genetically cross.

 

Recorded December 14, 2015

Music by Bobby Lee

Instagram: @tigerbelly

Twitter: @thetigerbelly
